summary: b l i n k | h.s imagines
body:
b l i n k | h.s imagines

a/n: im back snacks. im listening to lauv while writing this so—(which has ABSOLUTELY nothing to do with this imagine sooo) this doesn’t make any sense btw, besides the fact that it’s related to bp so yuh.

-

smiling cheekily at him, harry rose a suspicious brow that in turn made you giggle like a child in a candy store. shuffling your hands in your handbag, you dug for the two pieces of paper you had safely tucked inside. harry groaned and banged his head against the sofa with a longing sigh, “what is it now love?” he asked. grinning you continued to dig your hand in the bag, for a second worry set itself upon your shoulders when you couldn’t feel the paper but as soon as your hands tightly cluctched onto something that felt a lot like paper, you squealed, throwing yourself at your boyfriend of two years.

harry surprised at the sudden affection, chuckled lightly with a gaping mouth. he smirked and rolled his eyes, “ye extra touchy tonight y/n, could’ve just told meh ya know.” with his suggestive words, you blushed yet you didn’t stop yourself from slapping his shoulder and scolding him.

“keep your dirty mouth to yourself, harold.”

“but you love my dirty mouth on ye, don’t ya!”

growling, you huffed and kicked his feet, promptly glaring at him when your happy mood began to fade away. holding up his hands in a defensive way, he relaxed his muscles and scowled. you pinched the bridge of your nose while closing your eyes, then opened them and gave harry a look he was very much oh so familiar with.

“so guess what i got!” you squealed in utter delight. at the sight of you like this, harry couldn’t help himself and pinched your cheek quickly. pouting, you stuck your tongue out at him and shook your head in disappointment. harry returned the gesture in a mocking way which didn’t help from fueling down the flames in your body.

“what did ya get, pet?” his voice was laced with curiously as he spoke gruffly, green eyes staring at you as if he knew your every little secret.

grinning wolfishly at him, you showed him the two tickets you bought from last week, harry read the words written on the paper and quirked the corner of his mouth up a  bit, “ya makin’ me watch blankpink with ya?” he questioned in a manner which sounded child-like.

you softened and lunged for his warm chest, tucking yourself in. with a heart warming laugh, harry cradled you in his arms, his chin hovering above your head. harry smelt of expensive cologne and mint, something you very much loved. “please love, i wanna see them so bad!” you begged, “with you…” you continued.

“isn’t making me follow jennie in ig enough for ya y/n?” he teased, poking your sides which made you flinch and rise up from your comfortable position.

“well, a collab might come out of it.” you responded with no hesitation, harry’s eyes widened and he wasted no time from tickling your belly. he pushed you down on the coach with his long legs covered in black skinny jeans wrapping themselves around your hips as he pinned both of your arms with one hand and the other tickled your stomach, a tickle that made you squirm under him. as you laughed, tears drenched down from your eyes at pure ecstacy and you found yourself smiling brightly when harry joined you.

“now will you come with me, haze?” you asked, eyes fluttering up at him. harry snickered and shook his head saying, “can i ever say no to you love?” at the same time he pushed himself down so he could reach your plush lips.

let’s just say, that night, neither the two of you had clothes on.

-

BBMA voting Reminder

Just a little reminder to support Louis in his race against other artists for the Billboard Social Artist of the year. Voting starts today at 12 PM EST!! You can vote 100 times per day per platform per account. Please take some time out of ur day to vote! I know Louis has some intense competition and some of us may feel like it would be a waste if time, but maybe the other fandoms don’t see a threat and may not vote as well thinking they are a shoe in to win, and maybe we catch them sleeping. Maybe this time the Cinderella team wins!! Thanks. Ps. If ur a One Direction fan…this would be a great start and practice for teaming together to beat that other group 😘😉

summary: How about something where his gf’s in the crowd at his one of his shows and, like how other girls make signs he reads and shout...
question: How about something where his gf’s in the crowd at his one of his shows and, like how other girls make signs he reads and shout stuff that he picks up and responds too, she shouts things too only it’s like random shit intending to embarrass him and get him all flushed and flustered (not exactly in a too dirty way)
answer:
Okay!! Sorry it took me so long xxx I hope you like it, I changed it up a bit haha x

Harry saw his girlfriend in the crowd of fans. He spots her easily, after all she had a cute, mesmerizing face. 

He had just done performing Kiwi, and he’s out of energy at the moment. As he drank some water and the band are preparing the next song, Harry was on the stage casually responds to the signs that his fans brought.

One of them wrote: “I had more nipples than you!” 

Harry stared at the sign looking horrified, he asked that fan: “What? How many nipples do you have? I have four for god’s sake!”

“I have five!” That fan shouted, Harry’s eyes widen. “Oh my god.”

Everyone laughs.

Then Harry heard his baby love shouted something at him too.“Hey Harry!” 

He raised his eyebrow, couldn’t hide the smug he got on his lips. “Yeah, Darlin’?”

“You look like my next boyfriend!” She shouted to him, everyone beside her was giggling.

“Oh yeah? How about your current boyfriend?” Harry licked his lips and asked her. From the look on his face, she knew she’s in big trouble and possibly couldn’t get off bed tomorrow. But she still teased him. “I could drop him for you.”

“Is that so?” He squinted his eyes. Oh, this look. Y/N’s definitely not gonna get off bed tomorrow.

Masterlist

Harry stared at the sign looking horrified, he asked that fan: “What? How many nipples do you have? I have four for god’s sake!”

“I have five!” That fan shouted, Harry’s eyes widen. “Oh my god.”

Everyone laughs.

Then Harry heard his baby love shouted something at him too.“Hey Harry!” 

He raised his eyebrow, couldn’t hide the smug he got on his lips. “Yeah, Darlin’?”

“You look like my next boyfriend!” She shouted to him, everyone beside her was giggling.

“Oh yeah? How about your current boyfriend?” Harry licked his lips and asked her. From the look on his face, she knew she’s in big trouble and possibly couldn’t get off bed tomorrow. But she still teased him. “I could drop him for you.”

“Is that so?” He squinted his eyes. Oh, this look. Y/N’s definitely not gonna get off bed tomorrow.

Masterlist
